296
00:18:21,570 --> 00:18:23,070
Carolyn, what are you doing here?

297
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:26,270
I've been thinking, Harvey,
that if you loved this Monique woman so much...

298
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:28,970
Even you have to admit Kayla would be better off

299
00:18:28,970 --> 00:18:32,620
