00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:10,180
Talk things over.

342
00:21:10,220 --> 00:21:11,420
Harvey!

343
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:14,010
You're inconveniencing your customers.

344
00:21:14,020 --> 00:21:15,640
Get out here!

345
00:21:15,760 --> 00:21:17,700
Yeah, she's got hostages!

346
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:19,050
Oh, my God.

347
00:21:19,060 --> 00:21:21,400
Austin's there, and Julie!

348
00:21:21,410 --> 00:21:23,560
Get your ass out there before someone gets hurt!

349
00:21:23,570 --> 00:21:25,850
What am I, a moron? She'll shoot me.

350
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:28,950
She has got ten innocent people out there.

351
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:31,160
Sometimes you've got to take one for the team.

352
00:21:39,220 --> 00:21:41,360
Sweetie, it's mommy. I need to talk to daddy.

353
00:21:41,370 --> 00:21:43,450
Porter's hogging all the legos.

354
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:46,990
Tell 'em I said to share. Now put Daddy on.

355
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:51,710
