356
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:55,600
Put Daddy on, and I'll buy you a real robot.

357
00:21:55,610 --> 00:21:56,750
You will?

358
00:21:56,760 --> 00:22:00,760
A big one with laser beam eyes. Now go get Daddy!

359
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:02,590
I'm getting a real robot!

360
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,530
