369
00:22:53,230 --> 00:22:54,390
Sorry, store's closed.

370
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:56,180
Yeah, but there's a crazy woman in there!

371
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:58,270
Yeah, I know.

372
00:23:07,670 --> 00:23:09,080
Quick, turn on the TV.

373
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:10,890
It's kinda on the fritz.

374
00:23:10,900 --> 00:23:12,700
Well, turn on your radio.

375
00:23:12,710 --> 00:23:14,160
If only you'd come ten minutes earlier.

376
00:23:14,170 --> 00:23:17,280
Some woman is shooting up fields market.
She's got hostages.

377
00:23:17,290 --> 00:23:18,330
Oh, my God!

378
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:21,600
Yeah, we're all watching it over at Bree's house, and...

379
00:23:26,580 --> 00:23:28,630
