Oh, it's just awful. Deviled egg?

389
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:07,370
Oh, thank you.

390
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,680
I told you she'd have food.

391
00:24:19,590 --> 00:24:26,560
I'm sure some of you might be
thinking that this is all my fault

392
00:24:26,570 --> 00:24:29,880
