but I'm not. He is.

393
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:34,930
Will you people stop calling me?
I'm right in the middle of something.

394
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:38,170
He humiliated me.

395
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:41,330
First he cheated on me with
a stewardess named Monique.

396
00:24:41,340 --> 00:24:43,390
How cliché is that?

397
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:46,060
