398
00:24:46,070 --> 00:24:48,530
Now there are news trucks out there.

399
00:24:48,540 --> 00:24:51,200
Judy Pope's husband has an affair
nobody finds out.

400
00:24:51,210 --> 00:24:53,870
Mine cheats, and they break into programming!

