Tish, I'm sorry. I thought it was somebody else.

406
00:25:12,450 --> 00:25:15,480
Oh, my God, was that today? I'm so sorry.

407
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:17,580
I know, Tish. Yeah, I know.

408
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:19,270
I know I volunteered for the winter fair...

409
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:21,410
How can you look so calm?

410
00:25:21,660 --> 00:25:23,240
Aren't you scared?

411
00:25:23,540 --> 00:25:27,740
No, because I'm not gonna die today...

412
00:25:28,670 --> 00:25:30,840
and neither are you.

413
00:25:34,270 --> 00:25:36,460
Tish, I really don't think that I can.

414
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:40,410
I'm telling you, um...

415
