419
00:25:56,660 --> 00:25:57,560
Don't-- don't you do that?

420
00:25:57,570 --> 00:26:00,580
Oh, you mean our hostage exchange program?

421
00:26:00,590 --> 00:26:03,220
Okay, you don't have to be nasty.
My daughter is inside there.

422
00:26:03,230 --> 00:26:06,870
Ma'am, we're doing everything
we can to get her out safely.

423
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,750
Now please step back.

424
00:26:19,950 --> 00:26:22,870
